    style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<h2><strong>SOUKROM&Aacute;
    Z&Aacute;BAVA: <br /> SPORT A KULTURA</strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<em style=\"line-height:
